Capital Markets

Company Overview of Siebert Cisneros Shank & Co., L.L.C.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Siebert Cisneros Shank & Co., L.L.C. operates as an investment banking and financial services company. It offers investment banking and underwriting, financial advisory, and research and market analyses services to governments, institutions, and corporations in the United States. Siebert Cisneros Shank & Co., L.L.C. was formerly known as Siebert Brandford Shank & Co., L.L.C. The company was founded in 1996 and is based in New York, New York.


100 Wall Street18th FloorNew York, NY 10005United StatesFounded in 1996



