Siebert Cisneros Shank & Co. Appoints John Rhea as President of Its Corporate Finance and Capital Markets Division
Jun 20 17
Siebert Cisneros Shank & Co. announced appointed John Rhea as president of its corporate finance and capital markets division. Rhea, 51, is a senior advisor to the Boston Consulting Group and founder and managing partner of RHEAL Capital Management LLC. He will lead the corporate banking, sales and trading teams and continue the expansion of SCSCO's corporate finance business.


